  <brief_title>Effects of Aromatherapy on Anxiety in Invasive Radiologic Procedure</brief_title>
  <official_title>What is the Effect of Using Aromatherapy to Reduce Anxiety in Patients Undergoing Invasive Radiologic Procedures?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Carolinas Healthcare System</agency>
